UNIX BUILD
==========

Requirements
------------

You'll need the Gtk development headers.

Configure
---------

Default configure

$ ./configure

or specify one or more of the configure options:

$ ./configure --prefix=... --with-tcl=... --with-tk=... --with-glib-inc=... --with-glib-lib-inc=... --with-gtk-inc=... --with-gtk-lib-inc=... --with-pango-inc=... --with-cairo-inc=... --with-atk-inc=...

Check 'configure --help' for default values of the different options.

Build
-----

$ make

Install
-------

$ make install
